<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rich-adj">rich <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪtʃ/    美 /rɪtʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有钱的；富裕的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a rich nation 
富裕的国家</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>肥沃的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>rich soil 
肥沃的土地</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-rich-in">be rich in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在…方面丰富：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The country is rich in resources. 
这个国家资源丰富。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>richly /'rɪtʃli/ adv <br />
richness /'rɪtʃnəs/ n   </p></div>